item.title: CVE-2023-0602|2024-08-02T05:17:50.079Z -- unknown -- twittee%20text%20tweet
item.description: The Twittee Text Tweet WordPress plugin through 1.0.8 does not properly escape POST values which are printed back to the user inside one of the plugin's administrative page, which allows reflected XSS attacks targeting administrators to happen.
